{"tid":2348127,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁卓然離任前最後報告: 去年社會動盪令敏感複雜案件急增 部分檢控決定受不同立場人士質疑","createTime":"2020-12-31T13:23:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T13:43:33.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e31f19f4e1850148d6e72be138549c55e0a5cf45","tid":2348127,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:23:03.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】律政司刑事檢控科發表年報，回顧去年工作及重要案件。<br />\n<br />\n梁卓然最後一次以刑事檢控專員身份，向律政司司長提交報告，他指過去一年的社會動盪，令刑事檢控科處理的敏感複雜案件急增，部分檢控決定更受對政治光譜持不同立場的人士質疑。<br />\n<br />\n他在年報序言中，反駁有關公眾秩序活動案件檢控工作有拖延的指控，強調執法機關需時作進一步調查，同時被告亦會申請給予時間，在答辯前考慮證據及法律意見，因此大部分案件都要過一段時間才展開審訊，他批評有關指控是毫無根據，而指摘司法機構沒有從速排期也是無的放矢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=418620\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D418620&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhbKDDpXBBweeKWShnQU3kRY%3D&h=5e12b7af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D418620&h=cc3cc506\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=418620</a>"},{"pid":"2d268922cb5a8e5634dcdaf85dd64b9c75a200ec","tid":2348127,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:24:04.000Z","msg":"扮乜鳩呀？驚畜牲家人無得去外國下話"},{"pid":"88eca38b7eb6a2c1d13da202ac098006367254cd","tid":2348127,"uid":374427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:24:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CdcPZ4h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCdcPZ4h.jpg&h=5fbb89b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n推推行動post <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記唔記得上年除夕嗌：10 , 9 ...<br />\n<br />\n今年 除夕倒數&bull;和你嗌 !!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2345851\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2345851</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid"